data.description:
**Be sure to check out the 3-car garage accessible through a separate cul-de-sac around back (SW 117th St)**

This is a beautiful home that needs a little bit of touch-up to make it perfect, which is reflected in the below market price! It already has new carpet in the secondary bedrooms and new tile flooring in the kitchen. Come see this great home today! This home boasts 4 bedrooms, 3 bathrooms, a study, and a wealth of incredible features that set it apart from the rest. Massive primary bedroom with access to private back patio. Detached 3-car garage accessible through a secondary cul-de-sac around back, as well as tons of parking and a carport in the front of the property adds to the versatility of this home. There is a large backyard with a storage shed as well! To add to the outdoor living space, there is a patio off the living area in addition to the separate patio off the master bedroom, which means there's plenty of space to entertain! Two of the secondary bedrooms share a jack-and-jill bathroom, while the other bedroom has its own private bathroom, with private access to the carport. In addition to all of this versatility, this home is located in the Moore school district! Schedule your showing now to make this beautiful home yours!
